This paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of regularized optimal transport theory and convex optimization techniques suggests that this work may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions the use of histograms, which are commonly used in data science (cs.DS) and multimedia (cs.MM).
